text: Lee Eun-young is a South Korean taekwondo practitioner. She won a gold medal in lightweight at the 1987 World Taekwondo Championships in Barcelona. She won a gold medal at the 1988 Asian Taekwondo Championships, and a gold medal at the 1989 World Taekwondo Championships in Seoul. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:South Korean female taekwondo practitioners Category:World Taekwondo Championships medalists Category:Asian Taekwondo Championships medalists
